SUMMARY:Part Closure: LIONESS LINE: Saturday 16 and Sunday 17 August\, no 
 service between Euston and Watford Junction. There will also be no 
 BAKERLOO LINE service between Queens Park and Harrow & Wealdstone. Use 
 local London Buses services for South Hampstead and Kilburn High Road. 
 SOUTHERN services will continue to serve Harrow & Wealdstone and Watford 
 Junction on Saturday only. LONDON NORTH WESTERN RAILWAY services will 
 serve Euston\, Harrow & Wealdstone\, Bushey and Watford Junction on both 
 days. Special bus services operate.
